ActCanadian Space Agency Act
PrecisAppointment of LUC BRÛLÉ of Sainte-Julie, Quebec, to be President of the Canadian Space Agency on an interim basis, to hold office during pleasure, for a term of one year, or until such time as a new President is appointed, whichever is earlier, effective February 1, 2015.
